    <p>The Pitch</p>
    <p>Catch Ivan Heng, Gau­rav Kri­palani and Adrian Pang in this 20-minute short film, which tells of a mot­ley trio of theatre com­pa­nies that band to­gether to cre­ate an ur­gent project as the Covid-19 pan­demic rav­ages the­atres around the world . It is pro­duced by Wild Rice, Pangde­mo­nium and Sin­ga­pore Reper­tory Theatre. All do­na­tions will be split equally among the three com­pa­nies and sup­port in­di­vid­ual work, ed­u­ca­tion pro­grammes and out­reach ini­tia­tives.</p>
    <p>bit.ly/2QDRR5j</p>
    <p>Pre­mieres on Mon, 9pm</p>
    <p>Free but view­ers are en­cour­aged to do­nate at bit.ly/2EreBCU</p>


